TO SET UP THIS SCRIPT, YOU WILL NEED:

1.  A machine which is up at all the times you specify (ideally a web server),
  	running this script on a cron job at those times (ideally * * * * * for max flexibility).
	
2.	A Twitter application; create one at <https://dev.twitter.com/apps/new>;
    you'll need to put in the four keys; insert them into lines 145-148:

        $consumerKey  = '';
        $consumerSecret = '';
        $oAuthToken		= '';
        $oAuthSecret	= '';
    
3.  abraham's twitteroauth.php and OAuth.php, from
    <https://github.com/abraham/twitteroauth/tree/master/twitteroauth>;
    put them in the same directory.